<div class="existentialism-container">
    <div class="sartre-section">
        <div class="portraits">
            <div class="portrait-container">
                <img 
                    src="https://cdn.britannica.com/76/9476-050-6661C2E1/photograph-Jean-Paul-Sartre-Gisele-Freund-1968.jpg"
                    alt="Jean-Paul Sartre portrait"
                    class="sartre-portrait"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Rest of the component remains unchanged -->
        <div class="key-concepts">
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Existence Precedes Essence</h3>
                <div class="animation-container">
                    <div class="existence-animation">
                        <div class="being"></div>
                        <div class="essence"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Humans first exist, then through their actions and choices, create their essence. 
                    We are not born with a predetermined nature but must create ourselves through 
                    our choices.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Radical Freedom</h3>
                <div class="animation-container">
                    <div class="freedom-animation">
                        <div class="paths">
                            <div class="path"></div>
                            <div class="path"></div>
                            <div class="path"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="choice-point"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    We are "condemned to be free" - forced to make choices in every moment, 
                    with no external forces determining our decisions. This freedom brings 
                    both possibility and responsibility.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Authenticity</h3>
                <div class="animation-container">
                    <div class="authenticity-animation">
                        <div class="mask"></div>
                        <div class="true-self"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Living authentically means embracing our freedom and responsibility, 
                    facing the anxiety of choice rather than falling into bad faith or 
                    self-deception.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Morality & Freedom</h3>
                <div class="animation-container">
                    <div class="morality-animation">
                        <div class="scales">
                            <div class="scale left"></div>
                            <div class="scale right"></div>
                            <div class="balance-point"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="choice-ripples"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    In a world without predetermined moral values, each individual must 
                    create and uphold their own ethical framework through conscious choices 
                    and actions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="implications">
            <h3>Existential Implications</h3>
            <div class="implication-grid">
                <div class="implication">
                    <h4>Moral Responsibility</h4>
                    <p>
                        In a world without predetermined essence, we bear complete 
                        responsibility for our actions and their consequences.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="implication">
                    <h4>Meaning Creation</h4>
                    <p>
                        We must create our own meaning in an inherently meaningless 
                        universe, through our choices and commitments.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="implication">
                    <h4>Existential Anxiety</h4>
                    <p>
                        The weight of absolute freedom and responsibility creates 
                        anxiety, which we must confront rather than flee from.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .existentialism-container {
        padding: 2rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .sartre-section {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .portraits {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .portrait-container {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(var(--accent), 0.3), rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3));
        border-radius: 50%;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .portrait-container:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .sartre-portrait {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 4px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3);
    }

    .key-concepts {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 3rem 0;
    }

    .concept {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2);
    }

    .concept h3 {
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .animation-container {
        height: 150px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .existence-animation {
        position: relative;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .being {
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: emerge 4s infinite;
    }

    .essence {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at center,
            rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        animation: expand 4s infinite;
    }

    .freedom-animation {
        position: relative;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .paths {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .path {
        width: 2px;
        height: 0%;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.5);
        animation: grow 3s infinite;
    }

    .choice-point {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        bottom: 20%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    .authenticity-animation {
        position: relative;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .mask {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.8);
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: fade 4s infinite;
    }

    .true-self {
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    .morality-animation {
        position: relative;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .scales {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .scale {
        width: 60px;
        height: 4px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        position: absolute;
        transform-origin: center;
    }

    .scale.left {
        transform: rotate(-20deg);
        animation: balanceLeft 4s infinite;
    }

    .scale.right {
        transform: rotate(20deg);
        animation: balanceRight 4s infinite;
    }

    .balance-point {
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent));
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .choice-ripples {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at center,
            rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        animation: ripple 3s infinite;
    }

    .implications {
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .implication-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .implication {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .implication h4 {
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    @keyframes emerge {
        0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.8); opacity: 0.5; }
        50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.2); opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes expand {
        0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.2; }
        50% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0.4; }
    }

    @keyframes grow {
        0% { height: 0%; }
        100% { height: 100%; }
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
        50% { transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.2); }
    }

    @keyframes fade {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg); }
        50% { opacity: 0.2; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(180deg); }
    }

    @keyframes balanceLeft {
        0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-20deg); }
        50% { transform: rotate(20deg); }
    }

    @keyframes balanceRight {
        0%, 100% { transform: rotate(20deg); }
        50% { transform: rotate(-20deg); }
    }

    @keyframes ripple {
        0% { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0.8; }
        100% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0; }
    }
</style>